title: Foles’ Future and Potential Hard Knocks Teams
itunes:title: Foles’ Future and Potential Hard Knocks Teams
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all the latest news around the league including a mutual interest between Nick Foles and the Jaguars, (06:25) the chances of OBJ being traded from the Giants (12:17), and the 2019 kick off potential matchup that doesn’t include the Patriots (17:28). The heroes go through potential Hard Knocks teams for the coming season (22:34) and answer a few mailbag questions (36:47)
